messages.messageBody:
This is off topic but I don't know if any of you folks watched this
show. We've been catching reruns and loving it...kids too!. We
happened to just watch one titled "Active Listening"...where the parents
attend a class on the subject and try to practice it with their five
year old daughter. Very funny. Keeps your eyes out for it.
Amy
